何度でも復活し危険な城を探索

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Dead Cells is a celebration of perseverence: In this game, death is never final, but an essential learning tool. With every new run through ever-changing, enemy-infested levels, you get a little stronger and a little more skilled at overcoming relentless adversaries—and gradually overcome obstacles that once felt insurmountable. The acclaimed roguelike platformer makes all rewards feel earned; you'll be motivated to to brush off mistakes and charge back into battle again and again.
這款廣受好評的平台遊戲激勵你拋下錯誤，一次又一次地重新投入戰鬥。
This acclaimed platformer motivates you to to brush off mistakes and charge back into battle again and again.
高い評価を受けた横スクロール型のアクションゲームです。失敗を気にせず、倒されるたびにバトルに立ち向かう勇気を奮い起こしましょう。
這款屢獲殊榮的平台遊戲將不斷激勵你挑戰自我！即便失敗也無妨，因為每一次重來都是通往勝利的關鍵。
Ce jeu de plateforme acclamé vous motive à surmonter vos erreurs et à repartir à l’assaut encore et encore.
